   Politics &amp; Policy:
   U.S. Is Investigating All Failed Thrifts
   In Its Control for Ties to Milken, Drexel
   ----
   By Paulette Thomas
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/28/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A16
</SO>
